{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Scratchin' Melodii is a rhythm game about self expression.</strong> With gameplay inspired by the classic call-and-response roots of the rhythm game genre, your rival plays a beat, and you respond to it with your own! All in stylish fully animated songs that YOU control! (well, in your parts of it at least!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728050/extras/SprayFreestyle.gif?t=1734134360\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Melodii is a genderless young DJ who's gotten in trouble with the government for doing graffiti. Now owing community service, join Melodii on a ridiculous Funk &amp; Hip-Hop adventure where they'll make friends, enemies, and some sick freestyles. Do you have what it takes to be off the chart?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Satisfying rhythm gameplay with cool freestyle mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Funky original songs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique hand-drawn 2D animations for each song</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Loveable (okay some of them are kinda hateable) characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An RPG-inspired story mode to tie it all together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728050/extras/WavyMeal.gif?t=1734134360\" /></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728050/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734134360","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728050/page.bg.jpg?t=1734134360","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728050/9c91848ecbd9e08f27a880c8c8f474a8ab8ed226/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734134360","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it